vehicle
history
Get
a
professional
inspection
Book
a
pre
-
purchase

at
an
independent
or
authorised
service
Ask
the
mechanic
to
check
key
systems
:
engine
,
brakes
,
suspension
,
electronics
Request
written
notes
or
a
report
of
any
issues
found
Check
if
the
mileage
matches
Check
the
odometer
reading
against
the
mileage
in
the
report
Watch
for
signs
of
tampering
(
worn
pedals
,
suspicious
dashboard
fixes
)
Ask
the
seller
about
any
differences
Ask
for
service
records
Ask
the
seller
for
the
car
s
service
book
or
maintenance
records
Check
for
regular
oil
changes
,
filter
replacements
,
and
timing
belt
work
Note
any
missing
or
overdue
services
Take

real

drive

on
the

Drive

or

or

to

and
comfort

,

,

,

)
